类 MultiBucketCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.search.aggregations.BucketCollector
      • org.elasticsearch.search.aggregations.MultiBucketCollector
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.lucene.search.Collector
    public class MultiBucketCollector
extends BucketCollector
    A BucketCollector which allows running a bucket collection with several BucketCollectors. It is similar to the MultiCollector except that the wrap(org.elasticsearch.search.aggregations.BucketCollector...) method filters out the BucketCollector.NO_OP_COLLECTORs and not the null ones.

      • wrap

        public static BucketCollector wrap​(java.lang.Iterable<? extends BucketCollector> collectors)
        Wraps a list of BucketCollectors with a MultiBucketCollector. This method works as follows:
        • Filters out the BucketCollector.NO_OP_COLLECTORs collectors, so they are not used during search time.
        • If the input contains 1 real collector, it is returned.
        • Otherwise the method returns a MultiBucketCollector which wraps the non-BucketCollector.NO_OP_COLLECTOR collectors.
